## Title bar / page header rule (pick one)

- **Never show both** the layout title bar/header **and** a page-level header (e.g. `AppPageHeader`, sticky search bar) on the same screen.
- For each page, choose **one** approach:
  - **Use layout title bar**: rely on route meta (`title`, etc.) + layout header UI.
  - **Use in-page header**: set page meta to hide the layout title bar (e.g. `hideTopBar: true` where supported) and render the header within the page (sticky search/header, etc.).

